## Install npm and angular with docker

    > cd docker
    > make config #copy .env.dev to .env
    > make install #install node and angularng

## Setup new project

    > make console
    dc> ng new angular-app
    dc> cd angular-app

## Start server

    dc> cd angular-app
    dc> ng serve -H 0.0.0.0

## How view in browser

    > docker ps # get container id
    > docker inspect <container_id> # get container ip
    <container_ip>:4200
